-What?

543
00:26:00,060 --> 00:26:01,228
-RICHIE: Yeah, you sent me--
-No, no.

544
00:26:01,261 --> 00:26:02,295
-RICHIE: No, cousin--
-No. No, no, no.

545
00:26:02,329 --> 00:26:03,330
-I-I-I sent you there--
-RICHIE: No, cousin.

546
00:26:03,363 --> 00:26:04,732
You sent me there

547
00:26:04,765 --> 00:26:07,167
to fucking humiliate me,
