572
00:28:14,294 --> 00:28:15,629
Peeling mushrooms?

573
00:28:15,662 --> 00:28:18,098
Yeah. It's just
a nice little fun detail.

574
00:28:18,131 --> 00:28:20,067
So when the diners see it,
they know that someone

575
00:28:20,100 --> 00:28:21,368
